Area of parallelogram in java

[Area of parallelogram in java](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/area-of-parallelogram-in-java/)

Letâ€™s see program to find area of parallelogram in java.

import java.util.Scanner;
public class AreaOfParallelogram
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
      System.out.println("Please enter base of parallelogram: ");
      double base = sc.nextDouble();
      System.out.println("Please enter height of parallelogram: ");
      double height = sc.nextDouble();
      double area = base * height;
      System.out.println("Area of parallelogram is: " + area);
      sc.close();
   }
}
